Author: Mengchang Xu [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Mengchang Xu <xumengchang962@gmail.com>
Description: CNVision provides tools for copy number variation (CNV) detection 
    and visualization from sequencing data, including read counting, normalization, 
    segmentation, ploidy inference, and visualization.
